{"tid":2038816,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"馮智政：攬炒後香港民族全面西化是值得考慮","createTime":"2020-05-27T17:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T05:18:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"592da22462030ffab96ced952207b67567430928","tid":2038816,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"馮智政<br />\n<br />\n#EndGame? #梁啟超的全盤西化 美國取消香港特殊地位同Stand with HK people 後，我們首先要思考以及向外國遊說的，就是「香港與香港人」的分別。經濟制度、政策互動當然是香港範疇，但香港自由思想、香港學生福址、甚至是教育制度內進步價值及普世價值的宣揚，就是香港人的範疇。<br />\n<br />\n將「香港」淤泥污垢撤底清洗，留下「香港人」的精華以重生。<br />\n<br />\n攬炒又重生，攬抄勢在必行，我們開始準備重新建立時的地基是什麼。五四運動胡適倡議的全盤西化，絕對是一個可考慮的方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1382719615336493/posts/2445639695711141/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1382719615336493%2Fposts%2F2445639695711141%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32aarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=801d31cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1382719615336493/posts/2445639695711141/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fa9408a674e253cd7585ad17fba089c4b2aa3cd5","tid":2038816,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"馮智政幾時變左獨派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />???"},{"pid":"6bff67384aec23151f9313d3d079ea5cf778aade","tid":2038816,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9408a674e253cd7585ad17fba089c4b2aa3cd5","tid":2038816,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"馮智政幾時變左獨派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"伏兵啫"},{"pid":"48a9a181808d20ec62275a08274d429563a88fc7","tid":2038816,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9408a674e253cd7585ad17fba089c4b2aa3cd5","tid":2038816,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"馮智政幾時